text: When getting a dog puppy, I was told it’s mandatory to watch responsible ownership video by this company. Terms and conditions: company not responsible for anything, user responsible for everything, company can sell any user’s data. Disgusting.

Good to learn how to do urban planning. In this small museum, you can see the transition of Singapore from the very dirty place to such a modern city. The Singapore government does a very good job to plan their future, so if you are interested in urban planning, that's the place to go.
It's a division under NParks which manages training programs for the landscape sector, industry development and research programmes.
